 Packet style: 
[opcode][hiveNumber][hiveTemperature][hiveHumidity] 

Opcode: 8 bits 
Hive number: 1 to 10                  4 bits 
Hive Temperature: -40 C to 100 C      14 bits 
Hive Humidity: 0% to 100%             14 bits 

32 bits for values 
8 bits for opcode 
Total packet length/size is 40 bits 
